preparedMeals.name: Shrimp & Lobster Ravioli Grandi
preparedMeals.description: Creamy shrimp and lobster, all wrapped up. Need to get away? Our shrimp & lobster ravioli is a total trip. Authentic pasta crafted in Italy. Canadian lobster. And that shrimp! Made in Italy, each tender ravioli pillow is generously filled with MSC certified cold-water shrimp and lobster, along with a blend of butter, cream and chives. It’s rich, it’s creamy, and it is on the table in only 5 minutes – okay, 10 if you add a side salad. Best served with just a simple drizzle of extra-virgin olive oil to let all the flavours shine through. No journey. All destination.

preparedMeals.name: Cappellaci Beet & Goat Cheese
preparedMeals.description: You don’t have to travel to Italy to enjoy authentic pasta (although that would be great.) Our tender cappellacci (“little hats”) is expertly made by our renowned pasta supplier in Italy. Inside is a blend of sweet, fresh-tasting beetroot combined with rich goat milk cheese… made even richer with creamy ricotta. Each one is filled using a creative method that keeps the colourful layers separated for visual appeal. We’ve thought of everything. You can pick up the wine.

preparedMeals.name: Ravioli Grandi Butternut Squash & Brown Butter
preparedMeals.description: Large-sized egg pasta pockets are stuffed with a savoury-sweet filling of creamy butternut squash and nutty tasting brown butter. Give it a quick cook and toss with a lick of herbed olive oil or another favourite sauce – keep it simple enough to let the rich, yet delicate, flavours shine through. Our ravioli is on the table in less time than it takes to proclaim this to be your new favourite pasta (that’s less than 5 minutes). For a twist on holiday traditions, surprise your guests in the best way possible, serving simple bowls of authentic Italian pasta as an appetizer course.
